TITLE: Configure Ingress Annotations for Mattermost on AKS
DESCRIPTION: This YAML snippet configures Ingress annotations specifically tailored for Azure Application Gateway Ingress Controller (AGIC). It ensures that the Ingress resource is managed by AGIC and enforces SSL redirection for secure communication to the Mattermost instance.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/deploy/server/kubernetes/deploy-k8s-aks.rst#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
kubernetes.io/ingress.class: azure/application-gateway
appgw.ingress.kubernetes.io/ssl-redirect: "true"
```

