TITLE: Create MySQL User and Database
DESCRIPTION: This snippet creates a MySQL user named 'mmuser', a database named 'mattermost', and grants the user all privileges on the database. The user is identified by a password that should be changed to a more secure value. It is crucial for setting up the database before installing Mattermost.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/deploy/server/prepare-mattermost-mysql-database.rst#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
mysql> create user 'mmuser'@'%' identified by 'mmuser-password';
```

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
mysql> create database mattermost;
```

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
mysql> grant all privileges on mattermost.* to 'mmuser'@'%';
```

