TITLE: Enabling Mattermost Plugins with mmctl
DESCRIPTION: Enables specified plugins on the Mattermost server. It requires the plugins to be already installed. Multiple plugins can be enabled at once by listing their names after the `enable` command. This command directly interacts with the Mattermost server to activate the plugins.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/manage/mmctl-command-line-tool.rst#_snippet_120

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
mmctl plugin enable [plugins] [flags]
```

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
mmctl plugin enable hovercardexample pluginexample
```

