TITLE: config.json setting for AllowedUntrustedInternalConnections
DESCRIPTION: This setting whitelists local network addresses that the Mattermost server can request on behalf of a client. It's crucial for controlling untrusted requests within the local network, especially from integrations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/configure/environment-configuration-settings.rst#_snippet_107

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
".ServiceSettings.AllowedUntrustedInternalConnections": ""
```

