TITLE: Edit mmctl Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Opens the default editor defined in the EDITOR environment variable to modify the Mattermost server configuration. After editing, saving the file will upload the changes to the server. This command depends on the EDITOR environment variable being set.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/manage/mmctl-command-line-tool.rst#_snippet_53

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
mmctl config edit
```

