TITLE: SMTP Password Setting - Environment Variable
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows the environment variable to set the SMTP server password. String input is expected. This setting is used for authentication with the SMTP server and overrides `config.json`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/configure/environment-configuration-settings.rst#_snippet_75

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
``MM_EMAILSETTINGS_SMTPPASSWORD``
```

