TITLE: Refreshing OpenSearch Indices using Shell
DESCRIPTION: This command refreshes all indices in the OpenSearch cluster, making recent changes visible to search operations. It uses curl with the POST method and requires authentication.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/deploy/backup-disaster-recovery.rst#_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
curl -XPOST -u '<USERNAME>:<PASSWORD>' 'https://<HOSTNAME>/_refresh?pretty'
```

