TITLE: Granting Usage and Create Schema Privileges (PostgreSQL v15+)
DESCRIPTION: This SQL snippet grants usage and create schema privileges on the public schema to the 'mmuser' user, which is required for PostgreSQL v15 and later.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/deploy/server/preparations.rst#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
ALTER DATABASE mattermost OWNER TO mmuser;
GRANT USAGE, CREATE ON SCHEMA PUBLIC TO mmuser;
```

