TITLE: Enabling Console Log Output
DESCRIPTION: This setting configures Mattermost to output logs to the console.  It can be enabled/disabled via the System Console or through the `config.json` setting `.LogSettings.EnableConsole`, or the environment variable MM_LOGSETTINGS_ENABLECONSOLE. When enabled (true), log messages are written to stdout based on the console log level.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/configure/environment-configuration-settings.rst#_snippet_84

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
".LogSettings.EnableConsole": true",``
```

