TITLE: Configuration JSON Setting - Session Length AD/LDAP/Email
DESCRIPTION: Defines the session length in hours for users authenticated via AD/LDAP or email. The default value is 720 hours.  This setting affects how long a user's session remains active after they last entered their credentials via the web or desktop app when using email or AD/LDAP authentication.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/configure/environment-configuration-settings.rst#_snippet_93

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
".ServiceSettings.SessionLengthWebInHours: 720,"
```

