TITLE: Configure IAM Policy for OpenSearch Cross-Cluster Replication
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines the IAM policy required for enabling cross-cluster replication (CCR) in AWS OpenSearch. It grants permissions for ``es:ESHttp*`` and ``es:ESCrossClusterGet`` actions, allowing the OpenSearch cluster to communicate with another cluster for replication purposes. Replace `<region>`, `<acc_num>`, and `<domain_name>` with your actual AWS region, account number, and OpenSearch domain name respectively.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/deploy/backup-disaster-recovery.rst#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sh
