SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/upgrade/prepare-to-upgrade-mattermost.rst#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
UPDATE reactions SET channelid = COALESCE((select channelid from posts where posts.id = reactions.postid), '') WHERE channelid='';
```

