TITLE: Creating a compliance report using the Compliance API
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use the Mattermost Compliance API to create a new compliance report for a specific user within a given date range using curl. It requires authentication with a valid token and uses a JSON payload to specify report parameters such as the user's email, start and end times in Unix Epoch format.  `yi94pwci6ibjfc9phbikhqutbe` should be replaced with the actual token value, and dates should be converted to epoch format.
