TITLE: Updating ThreadTeamId Column - SQL
DESCRIPTION: This SQL script updates the 'ThreadTeamId' column in the 'Threads' table using data from the 'Channels' table.  It sets the 'ThreadTeamId' to the 'TeamId' from 'Channels' where the 'ChannelId' in 'Threads' matches the 'Id' in 'Channels' and where 'ThreadTeamId' is currently NULL. This populates the new column with the appropriate team ID for each thread.
