TITLE: Accessing WebRTC Internals in Chrome
DESCRIPTION: Opens the `chrome://webrtc-internals/` page in the Chrome browser. This provides detailed information about the WebRTC connection, including audio and video streams, signaling data, and statistics. This tool is helpful for diagnosing audio/video issues during active calls.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/collaborate/make-calls.rst#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
chrome://webrtc-internals/
```

