TITLE: Installing Python Packages with Pipenv
DESCRIPTION: This command uses `pipenv` to install the Python packages specified in the project's Pipfile and Pipfile.lock files, including development dependencies. These packages are required for building the Mattermost documentation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/README.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
pipenv install --dev
```

