TITLE: SAML User Migration Example (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This JSON configuration provides an example of the expected format for a user mapping file used during SAML authentication migration. Each object represents a user and includes their email address along with SAML-specific authentication data (IDP ID and SAML user ID).
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/docs/blob/master/source/manage/mmctl-command-line-tool.rst#_snippet_176

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
[
    {
      "email": "user1@example.com",
      "auth_data": {
        "saml": {
          "idp_id": "saml_idp_1",
          "saml_user_id": "user123"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "email": "user2@example.com",
      "auth_data": {
        "saml": {
          "idp_id": "saml_idp_2",
          "saml_user_id": "user456"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
```
